1. *Sada* se svi uče na daljinu. (Now everyone is learning online.)
2. *Sada* je pravo vreme za započinjanje novog projekta. (Now is the right time to start a new project.)
3. Njegov prijatelj *sada* živi u inostranstvu. (His friend now lives abroad.)
4. Ona *sada* radi u velikoj kompaniji. (She now works at a big company.)
5. *Sada* bi trebalo da naučiš novi jezik. (Now you should learn a new language.)
6. Oni *sada* odlaze na more. (They are now going to the sea.)